		"Name": "Helepolis",
		"Details": "While derived from the double Thumper armed HEP-2I, the Helepolis HEP-2PAI is only armed with a single Field Kannone for the artillery role.  This was done to allow easier reconfiguration in the field since out in the periphery you never know what you will be able to repair your mech with.  This feature also makes it a field expediant to switch the Field Kannone from Left to Right side during a major rebuild.  Saving time and effort.\n\n <b><color=#e51717>Pafftek Industries Sub-mod</color></b>",
		"Icon": "uixTxrIcon_helepolis"
	},
